		</a></li><li class="link"><a href="javascript: void(0);" data-share-type="link" class="glyph-link">Link</a></li><li class="whatsapp"><a href="javascript: void(0);" data-share-type="whatsapp" class="glyph-whatsapp">WhatsApp</a></li><li class="print"><a href="https://decorrespondent.nl/article/5212/print" target="_blank" class="glyph-print">Print</a></li><li class="pdf"><a href="https://decorrespondent.nl/article/5212.pdf" target="_blank" class="glyph-pdf">PDF</a></li></ul><div class="clear"></div><a class="close glyph-cross-bold" href="javascript:void(0);"></a></div></div></li><li class="save-publication"><a title="Bewaar deze publicatie" href="javascript:void(0);" class="save-publication-api" data-article-id="5212"><span class="glyph-bookmark"></span><span class="glyph-checkmark-small"></span><span class="glyph-cross-small"></span><span class="save-text">Bewaar</span><span class="saved-text">Bewaard</span></a></li><li class="publication-date"><span class="glyph-time"></span><time data-field="date" datetime="2016-09-08" title="8-9-2016 10:45">
